          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">R<hi rend="small-caps">E</hi><hi rend="small-caps">TURNING</hi> Janus now prepares,</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-2" n="2">For Bec, a new supply of cares,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-3" n="3">Sent in a bag to Doctor Swift,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-4" n="4">Who thus displays the New-year's-gift.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-5" n="5"><lb/>First, this large parcel brings you tidings</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-6" n="6">Of our good Dean's eternal chidings;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-7" n="7">Of Nelly's pertness, Robin's leasings,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-8" n="8">And Sheridan's perpetual teazings.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-9" n="9">This box is cramm'd on ev'ry side</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-10" n="10">With Stella's magisterial pride.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-11" n="11">Behold a cage with sparrows fill'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-12" n="12">First to be fondled, then be kill'd.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-13" n="13">Now to this hamper I invite you,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-14" n="14">With six imagin'd cares to fright you.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-15" n="15">Here in this bundle Janus sends</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-16" n="16">Concerns by thousands for your friends:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-17" n="17">And here's a pair of leathern pokes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-18" n="18">To hold your cares for other folks.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-19" n="19">Here from this barrel you may broach</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-20" n="20">A peck of troubles for a coach.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-21" n="21">This ball of wax your ears will darken,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-22" n="22">Still to be curious, never hearken.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-23" n="23">Lest you the town may have less trouble in,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-24" n="24">Bring all your Quilca cares to Dublin,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-25" n="25">For which he sends this empty sack;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-753-CWJS-line-26" n="26">And so take all upon your back.</l>
          </lg>
